
Creative Tabs
1. ModCreativeModeTabs
    * New Tab - Copy and Paste Line 16-27
        * Rename Tab for Corresponding Lines 16 and 17(name?)
        * Change Tab Icon by editing line 18
        * Change Line 19 to change Tab name
            * "Create Translation" aka Add name to en_us.json
        * Add/Remove Items from Tab by Editing Line 21-24


Items:
1. ModModelProvider
    * Copy line 22 - Generates Model
2. ModItems
    * Line 18 - Creates a New Item
    * Line 32 - Selects Creative Mode Tab
        *  Line 35 - Adds item to Selected Creative Mode Tab
3. lang, en_us.json
    * Line 2 - Renames Item in game
4. Add textures
    * Drag files into directory
5. DataGen


